# AFS Asana

## Authentication [/]

### Signup [POST /auth/signup]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (UserAuthPayload)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (AuthenticatedUserResponse)

### Login [POST /auth/login]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (UserAuthPayload)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (AuthenticatedUserResponse)

+ Response 401

+ Response 404

## Workspaces [/workspaces]

### Create Workspace [POST /workspaces]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
    
            Authorization: Bearer jsonWebToken
            
    + Attributes (CreateWorkspacePayload)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (CreatedWorkspaceResponse)

+ Response 401

### Get Workspace [GET /workspaces/{workspaceId}]

+ Parameters

    + workspaceId: uuid (string)

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
    
            Authorization: Bearer jsonWebToken

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (CreatedWorkspaceResponse)

+ Response 401

+ Response 404

### Add User to Workspace [POST /workspaces/{workspaceId}/addUser]

+ Parameters

    + workspaceId: uuid (string)

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
    
            Authorization: Bearer jsonWebToken
            
    + Attributes (UserWorkspacePayload)

+ Response 200

+ Response 401

+ Response 404

### Remove User from Workspace [POST /workspaces/{workspaceId}/removeUser]

+ Parameters

    + workspaceId: uuid (string)

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
    
            Authorization: Bearer jsonWebToken
            
    + Attributes (UserWorkspacePayload)

+ Response 200

+ Response 401

+ Response 404

