## Data Structures

### UserAuthPayload (object)
+ data
    + email: me@example.com
    + password: password

### AuthenticatedUserResponse (object)
+ data
    + id: uuid (string)
    + token: token (string)

### CreateWorkspacePayload (object)
+ data
    + name: workspaceName

### CreatedWorkspaceResponse (object)
+ data
    + id: uuid (string)
    + name: workspaceName (string)

### UserWorkspacePayload (object)
+ data
    + id: uuid (string) - Id of user to add/remove

### CreateTeamPayload (object)
+ data
    + name: teamName

### CreatedTeamResponse (object)
+ data
    + id: uuid (string)
    + name: teamName (string)

### UserTeamPayload (object)
+ data
    + id: uuid (string) - Id of user to add/remove

### CreateProjectPayload (object)
+ data
    + name: projectName
    + teamId: uuid

### CreatedProjectResponse (object)
+ data
    + id: uuid (string)
    + name: projectName (string)

### UserProjectPayload (object)
+ data
    + id: uuid (string) - Id of user to add/remove

### CreateTaskPayload (object)
+ data
    + name: taskName
    + projectId: uuid

### CreatedTaskResponse (object)
+ data
    + id: uuid (string)
    + name: taskName (string)

### ListOfTasksReponse (object)
+ data (array)
    + (object)
        + id: uuid (string)
        + name: taskName (string)
